  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a hotel room. Find the anomaly and break free from the loop.<br><br><strong>Find anomalies. </strong><br> <br><strong>Fix anomalies. </strong><br> <br><strong>Get out from the Loop.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.poster.avif?t=1747834809\" width=480 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.webm?t=1747834809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.mp4?t=1747834809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Room Stalker is a short walking simulator inspired by The Exit 8, Luxury Dark, and I'm on Obeservation Duty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is available in English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese and Indonesian.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~60 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Fix Anomaly】<br>  You can point to the anomaly to fix the anomaly. <br><br>【Object Inspector】<br>  Observe objects to find out the background about this place. <br><br>【Loop】<br>  The further you walk, the more scary and dangerous the loop becomes.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a hotel room. Find the anomaly and break free from the loop.<br><br><strong>Find anomalies. </strong><br> <br><strong>Fix anomalies. </strong><br> <br><strong>Get out from the Loop.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.poster.avif?t=1747834809\" width=480 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.webm?t=1747834809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639000/extras/f51f3ccd290abc142c85eb10355de293.mp4?t=1747834809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Room Stalker is a short walking simulator inspired by The Exit 8, Luxury Dark, and I'm on Obeservation Duty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is available in English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese and Indonesian.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~60 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Fix Anomaly】<br>  You can point to the anomaly to fix the anomaly. <br><br>【Object Inspector】<br>  Observe objects to find out the background about this place. <br><br>【Loop】<br>  The further you walk, the more scary and dangerous the loop becomes.</p>",
